description:
Learn how to read tarot cards quickly and easily. Tarot is a book full of illustrated symbols that have a reading for each person and each question. It can serve you to learn details of the past, present or future.
In this guide you will find the meaning of each card and the main spreads to solve all kinds of issues. You have examples of spreads to start your journey reading tarot cards.
name: Tarot Cards: Discover the meaning
intro: Detailed guide for beginners to the universe of tarot and its reading. Learn the meaning of each card and the most famous and commonly used spreads.
